(format-conversion). The REFIT cross-sections are preserved in    4849 1451
ENDF provided that NJOY-compatible channel- and scattering-radius 4849 1451
options have been chosen by the REFIT evaluator. Conversion below 4849 1451
is rigorous/exact because of such compatibility.                  4849 1451
